content: Brown-Iron Cart is a Yaoguai Chief boss fight that you'll go up against at the start of Chapter 5 in Black Myth: Wukong. Blocking the pathway from the Ashen Pass to the Camp of Seasons, the cart is just one of the Five Element Carts you'll need to fight in this Chapter.

Brown-Iron Cart is a Yaoguai Chief boss fight that you'll go up against at the start of Chapter 5 in Black Myth: Wukong. Blocking the pathway from the Ashen Pass to the Camp of Seasons, the cart is just one of the Five Element Carts you'll need to fight in this Chapter.
